bill.summary: 5/6/1993--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to suspend, through December 31, 1994, the duty on naphth (2,1-d)-1,2,3-oxadiazole-5-sulfonic acid and its sodium salt.
